  <testcase name="document_idempotency_pattern" classname="com.techleadguru.phase3.day53.Day53IdempotencyKeysTest" time="0.007">
    <system-out><![CDATA[[DAY 53] IDEMPOTENCY KEY PATTERN:

  PROBLEM: Network retry causes duplicate charge
    POST /payments (timeout) → retry → charged TWICE

  SOLUTION:
    1. Client generates UUID: X-Idempotency-Key: 550e-...
    2. Server checks key in Redis: seen before?
       → YES: return cached response (no DB write)
       → NO: process, store result under key (TTL=24h)
    3. Client retries with same key → gets same paymentId

